<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-gold font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-3">July 3, 2026</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">The Countdown Is On</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Two column layout -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Fifty years ago, Washington, D.C. stood at the center of one of the most memorable
          celebrations in American history: the Bicentennial of the United States. It was a moment
          of grandeur, pride, and patriotism that left an indelible mark on a generation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          July 4, 2026 marks the 250th anniversary of the United States of America — a milestone
          that will only occur once in our lifetimes. Across the country, communities will celebrate
          this extraordinary moment. But in Washington, D.C., the celebration begins the night before,
          when thousands gather to launch the historic anniversary weekend.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          The Countdown 250 Ball brings together leaders, heroes, entertainers, and
          proud Americans for a night of patriotism, inspiration, and celebration.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-navy">
          Be there when history is made.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="/countdown250/images/event-photos/aab-2025-vip-group-formal.jpg"
          alt="VIP group at the All-American Inaugural Ball 2025"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full object-cover aspect-[4/3]"
        />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-navy/10 rounded-lg -z-10"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
